Title: Discovery page: Improve escaping of services when creating disabled services rules
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1604995730
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0i2

Previous versions of Checkmk were escaping too many character, like the " " space, when
creating a disabled services rule by clicking on "Move to disabled services" for a single
service on the service discovery page.
